contentrichtext.text: {{Use dmy dates|date=October 2012}} {{Infobox Australian place | type = suburb | name = Oakleigh East | city = Melbourne | state = vic | image = | caption = | alternative_location_map = Australia Victoria metropolitan Melbourne |longd=145.112|latd=37.896 | lga = [[City of Monash|Monash]] | postcode = 3166 | pop = 5,972 (2011) | area = 2.1 | est = | stategov = [[Electoral district of Oakleigh|Oakleigh]] | fedgov = [[Division of Chisholm|Chisholm]] | dist1 = 16 | location1= [[Melbourne city centre|Melbourne]] | near-nw = [[Chadstone, Victoria|Chadstone]] | near-n = [[Mount Waverley, Victoria|Mount Waverley]] | near-ne = [[Mount Waverley, Victoria|Mount Waverley]] | near-w = [[Oakleigh, Victoria|Oakleigh]] | near-e = [[Clayton, Victoria|Clayton]] | near-sw = [[Oakleigh, Victoria|Oakleigh]] | near-s = [[Huntingdale, Victoria|Huntingdale]] | near-se = [[Clayton, Victoria|Clayton]] }} '''Oakleigh East''' is a [[suburb]] of [[Melbourne]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]], [[Australia]] 16 km south-east of Melbourne's [[Melbourne city centre|central business district]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Oakleigh East, Victoria|url=http://www.postcodes-australia.com/areas/vic/mulgrave/oakleigh+east|work=Postcodes Australia|accessdate=23 November 2011}}</ref> Its [[Local government areas of Victoria|local government area]] is the [[City of Monash]]. At the [[Census in Australia#2011|2011 Census]], Oakleigh East had a population of 5,972.<ref name="abs">{{Census 2011 AUS | id = SSC21049 | name = Oakleigh East | accessdate = 21 June 2012 | quick = on}}</ref> ==History== An Oakleigh East Post Office opened on 15 June 1918 on Huntingdale Road near Huntingdale (then East Oakleigh) railway station. This was renamed Huntingdale around 1955. In 1967 another Oakleigh East office opened on Huntingdale Road north of [[Dandenong Road]] ([[Princes Highway]]).<ref name = "a">{{Citation| last = Premier Postal History | title = Post Office List | url = https://www.premierpostal.com/cgi-bin/wsProd.sh/Viewpocdwrapper.p?SortBy=VIC&country= | accessdate = 11 April 2008 }}</ref> ==References== {{Reflist}} {{City of Monash suburbs}} [[Category:Suburbs of Melbourne]] {{Melbourne-geo-stub}}
